rice Merleau-Ponty. The book also includes many photos documenting McTavish's physical transformation.  aMode of access: Internet via World Wide Web.  aIn English.0 aDescription based on online resource; title from PDF title page (publisher's Web site, viewed 26. Mrz 2024) 0aFeminism and sports. 0aFeminismxHistoryx21st century. 0aFeminismxHistoryy21st century. 0aFeminism. 0aPhysical fitness. 0aWomen bodybuilders. 4aCultural Studies : Cultural Studies. 4aGender and Sexuality : Feminist. 4aGender and Sexuality : Gender Studies. 4aGender and Sexuality : Women's Studies. 4aSociology : Sports and Society. 7aSOCIAL SCIENCE / Women's Studies.2bisacsh40uhttps://doi.org/10.1515/978143845478840uhttps://www.degruyter.com/isbn/9781438454788423Coveruhttps://www.degruyter.com/document/cover/isbn/9781438454788/original  aGBV-deGruyter-alles